---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — YOUTUBE PLAYABLES" description="Learn more about YOUTUBE PLAYABLES — our mission, editorial standards, and why we build free browser-native games.">
  <a href="#main" class="skip-link">Skip to content</a>
  <main id="main" class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">About YOUTUBE PLAYABLES.</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-7 text-body">YOUTUBE PLAYABLES is a free, browser-native gaming platform built for people who want to play instantly — no downloads, no accounts, no friction. We focus on clean gameplay, thoughtful design, and honest descriptions so you can find a game that matches your mood in seconds.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Our mission</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-body">Make high-quality HTML5 games accessible to everyone. We believe casual play supports cognitive fitness, stress relief, and social connection — and that the best games respect your time, device, and privacy.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Editorial standards</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-body">Every game description, guide, and article is written to be accurate, original, and useful. We update content when games change, and we avoid filler, keyword stuffing, or automated fluff. If something is unclear, we rewrite it.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Privacy first</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-body">We do not sell personal data. High scores and recently played games are stored only in your browser’s local storage. No account is required to play. Read the full <a href="/privacy" class="text-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for details.</p>

    <a href="/playables" class="mt-10 inline-block text-sm text-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline">← Back to playables</a>
  </main>
</Layout>
